==German==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|goh|de}} {{m|goh|sehan}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|de}} {{m|gem-pro|*sehwaną}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|de}} {{m|ine-pro|*sekʷ-||to see}}. Compare Low German {{m|nds|sehn}}, Dutch {{m|nl|zien}}, English {{m|en|see}}, Danish {{m|da|se}}, Gothic {{m|got|𐍃𐌰𐌹𐍈𐌰𐌽}}.

